Class SharedPreferencesUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aj.android.commons.app.SharedPreferencesUtils

  • public class SharedPreferencesUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Collection of utilities related SharedPreferences, use this for quick saving and retrieving information from shared preferences.
    Author:
    Akhil Jain
